OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying very
OL,6,Fwarm and humid overnight. Dry for most
OL,7,Fbut elevated thunderstorms possible
OL,8,Fovernight and in the early hours of
OL,9,Fthe morning. These could turn gusty
OL,10,Fwith hail and thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAlthough temperatures falling,
OL,13,Fstaying very warm with humidity levels
OL,14,Fremaining high. Clear skies in the
OL,15,Fnorth but low cloud moving into the
OL,16,Fsouthwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
